            <history-note id="DLM320635">Subsection <amended-provision>(1)(c)</amended-provision> was <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, as from <amendment-date>3 May 2001</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM90184">section 9</amending-provision> <amending-leg>Companies Act 1993 Amendment Act 2001</amending-leg> (2001 No 18) <amending-instruction>by substituting the expression <quote.in quote="1">301, 383, and 385</quote.in> for the expression <quote.in quote="1">and 301 of this Act</quote.in></amending-instruction>.</history-note>
