            <history-note id="DLM322347">Subsection <amended-provision>(7)(b)</amended-provision> was <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, as from <amendment-date>3 June 1998</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM426285">section 16(2)</amending-provision> <amending-leg>Companies Amendment Act 1998</amending-leg> (1998 No 31) <amending-instruction>by inserting the word <quote.in quote="1">; and</quote.in></amending-instruction>.</history-note>
