            <history-note id="DLM1101425"><amended-provision>Section 373(4)(j)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>added</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 November 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM389294">section 39(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Companies Amendment Act 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 56).</history-note>
