            <history-note id="DLM323238">Subsection <amended-provision>(2)(21)</amended-provision> was <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, as from <amendment-date>18 June 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM392173">section 13</amending-provision> <amending-leg>Companies Amendment Act (No 2) 2006</amending-leg> (2006 No 62). <emphasis style="italic">See</emphasis> <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM435272">clause 2(1)</extref> Companies Amendment Act (No 2) 2006 Commencement Order 2007 (SR 2007/108)</citation>.</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM323239">Subsection <amended-provision>(2)(22)</amended-provision> was <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, as from <amendment-date>15 April 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM244149">section 21(2)</amending-provision> <amending-leg>Companies Amendment Act (No 2) 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 24) <amending-instruction>by substituting <quote.in quote="1">210(7)</quote.in> for <quote.in quote="1">210(2)</quote.in></amending-instruction>.</history-note>
